<hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid var(--border); margin: 26px 0;" />

<h2>Assisi (Full day)</h2>
<p>
	One of Umbria’s most famous towns, with major basilicas, beautiful stone streets and a lot of history. Plan a full day so you can explore at a relaxed pace
	(and avoid rushing the main sights). For a first time visit we recommend using the tourist bus which stops at the bottom, middle and top of the town. Otherise is is a lot of steep walking under the summer sun. 
</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Type:</strong> Full day</li>
	<li><strong>Drive time:</strong> ~1 hour</li>
	<li>
		<strong>Recommended parking:</strong>{" "}
		<a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/E7b4AsBRst5zVsoW7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Maps link</a>{" "}
		— easiest access, with an elevator up into Assisi
	</li>
</ul>
