<h2>Siena (Full day / overnight)</h2>
<p>
	A classic Tuscan city for architecture, food and atmosphere—worth a full day, or even an overnight if you want to take it slower.
</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Type:</strong> Full day / overnight</li>
	<li><strong>Drive time:</strong> ~1 hour</li>
	<li><strong>Recommended parking:</strong> (TBD)</li>
